                <li><a href="/prototypes/onboard-survey/version-2/SEFT/load-collection-instruments-ready.html">Upload is complete with no errors</a></li>
                <li><a href="/prototypes/onboard-survey/version-2/SEFT/load-collection-instruments-errors.html">Upload is complete, some files have errors</a></li>
            </ol>
            <p>Simplified design</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Added SEFT/eQ option when setting up survey</li>
                <li>Removed multimode (Split add eQ and SEFT at survey creation)</li>
                <li>Removed eQ ID</li>
                <li>Single column CI manage screen</li>
                <li>Replaced drop-downs with radio buttons</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Version 1</h3>
            {{ 
                onsButton({
                    "type": 'button',
